text: An hunda hida to Ciltancumba, to Hysseburnan, & to Hwitcyrcan hunendlyftig hida.

To Uferantune XL hida to Cleran X, to Alresforda XL, to Crawelea II læs XXX, to Þudatuna XX, to Aclea X, to twam Polhæmatunan X, to Myceldefer X, to Endefer X, æt Abbodestun X, to Crundelan L, et Beonytlege X, to Drocelesford XVII, æt Byrhfunt, & æt Hafunt X, to Fearham XXX, to Þealtham, & æt Myceldefer L, Oðerhealf to Faleðlea.
<../images/tbar.gif>is ealles fif hund hida & ehta & hundseofontig hida.
